description:
we reckon the amount of dnm chats we see happening outside messina stores over a couple of scoops has got to be one of the highest of any hospo establishment in aus.

SO for R U OK? day we've popped some envelopes outside every messina store in nearby hidden locations (swipe for some hints) for you to find, with two single scoop vouchers in each. bring them in store with a mate and share some gelato on us over a good chat ðŸ™‚

they're out there NOW so swing by any store asap. and please don't forget you don't need a special day to ask your mate if they're OK, but we can use this day as a reminder to do it more often ðŸ«¶

t&c: if you find a voucher, it cannot be exchanged for cash. only valid on 2 x 1 scoop serves redeemed at the same time. one voucher per customer.
